00:11:17.020 --> 00:11:19.860
"Is there a reason/explanation
that Docs that are in a public

00:11:19.860 --> 00:11:22.010
folder on Drive aren't
accessible using

00:11:22.010 --> 00:11:27.220
googledrive.com?"
