00:11:41.310 --> 00:11:43.540
We have a page dedicated
to publishing

00:11:43.540 --> 00:11:45.860
website content on Drive.

00:11:45.860 --> 00:11:51.640
The requirements are that you
set the folder as public.

00:11:51.640 --> 00:11:54.660
And according to the question,
the folder was public.

00:11:54.660 --> 00:11:56.020
