like this--

00:12:20.530 --> 00:12:25.560
https://googledr
ive.com/host/folderid.

00:12:25.560 --> 00:12:31.940
And for instance, if you have
images in that folder, your

00:12:31.940 --> 00:12:34.605
full complete URL to the image
will be googledrive.com/

00:12:34.605 --> 00:12:35.855
host/folderid/im
ages/kittens.jpg.

00:12:40.510 --> 00:12:46.550
So there is a way to publish
files from a public folder.

00:12:46.550 --> 00:12:51.230
And they're accessible from
googledrive.com when the

00:12:51.230 --> 00:12:52.300
folder is public.

